CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774980701
OL,3,CNightclub linked to deadly meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak in Kent to re-open
OL,6,FThe nightclub at the centre of a
OL,7,Fdeadly meningitis outbreak in
OL,8,FCanterbury, in Kent, has announced it
OL,9,Fis to re-open this week.
OL,11,FClub Chemistry has been shut since
OL,12,FMarch 15, but has now announced it
OL,13,Fwill re-open on Thursday (April 2).
OL,15,FThe club's owner, Louise Jones-
OL,16,FRoberts, told ITV Meridian she feels
OL,17,Fit is "safe" to resume trading,
OL,18,Ffollowing advice from the UK Health
OL,19,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774980701
OL,3,CNightclub linked to deadly meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak in Kent to re-open
OL,6,FShe said: "The UKHSA have reduced the
OL,7,Frisk factor, so they're confident that
OL,8,Fthe incubation period for any of the
OL,9,Fperiods of time that we were looking
OL,10,Fat previously has passed.
OL,12,F"So, we feel that it's safe to do."
OL,14,FTwo students died after an outbreak of
OL,15,Fmeningitis in Canterbury earlier in
OL,16,FMarch, while more than a dozen others
OL,17,Fwere admitted to hospital for
OL,18,Ftreatment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774980701
OL,3,CNightclub linked to deadly meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak in Kent to re-open
OL,6,FStaff, in anticipation of the venue's
OL,7,Fre-opening, have carried out two
OL,8,F"thorough cleans, one including the
OL,9,Fuse of medical grade products and high-
OL,10,Ftemperature sanitation on all key
OL,11,Fareas," Club Chemistry said in a
OL,12,Fstatement.
OL,14,FIt added that Environmental Health
OL,15,Fofficers and Public Health England had
OL,16,Falso both been invited to inspect the
OL,17,Fpremises.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774980701
OL,3,CNightclub linked to deadly meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak in Kent to re-open
OL,6,F"Their verdict: our standards were
OL,7,Foutstanding, and they were unable to
OL,8,Fsuggest a single improvement," the
OL,9,Fstatement read.
OL,11,FMs Jones-Roberts, when asked about
OL,12,Fwhat kind of community response she
OL,13,Fexpects to Thursday's re-opening, said
OL,14,Fher staff are ready to welcome
OL,15,Fcustomers back "when they are ready".
OL,17,FShe said: "Our take on it, is that two
OL,18,Fyoung people have lost their lives,
OL,19,Fand for us now we are a place for
OL,20,Fpeople to come together and have
OL,21,Fshared experiences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774980701
OL,3,CNightclub linked to deadly meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak in Kent to re-open
OL,6,F"But, ultimately, now I think our role
OL,7,Fis to make sure that those two lives
OL,8,Fmean something going forwards in terms
OL,9,Fof protection of other young people,
OL,10,Fso the same thing can't happen again.
OL,12,F"What we've said to people is that 'we
OL,13,Fare really cognisant of the anxiety
OL,14,Fand the fear around this and we are
OL,15,Fready for people when they are ready,'
OL,16,Fand that's it.
OL,18,F"We're not pushing anything, we're not
OL,19,Fasking, we're here."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774980701
OL,3,CNightclub linked to deadly meningitis
OL,4,Coutbreak in Kent to re-open
OL,6,FThousands of students living on the
OL,7,FUniversity of Kent campus have been
OL,8,Foffered vaccinations, in the wake of
OL,9,Fthe meningitis outbreak.
OL,11,FThe inoculation program has also be
OL,12,Fexpanded to include some Year 11
OL,13,Fpupils at schools in Kent affected by
OL,14,Fthe outbreak.
OL,16,FThe latest update from the UKHSA
OL,17,Fshowed that, as of Thursday, March 26,
OL,18,Fsome 22 cases of meningitis - 20
OL,19,Fconfirmed and two under investigation
OL,20,F- had been reported in Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
